    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RE-EXIT</strong> 是一款以异常现象为主题的恐怖游戏，会考验你的感知能力和对细节的专注度。你被一场无法解释的异常所引发的时间循环困住，你的任务是仔细观察周围环境、设法生存下来，并报告任何异常情况，寻找逃离的方法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>玩法概览：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>异常检测：</strong> 每当循环重置时，都要仔细检查走廊是否出现变化。异常可能<strong>细微</strong>也可能<strong>明显</strong>，极大考验你的观察力。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/5a75e6621715341e08c0a22a319cfc81.poster.avif?t=1764446994\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/5a75e6621715341e08c0a22a319cfc81.webm?t=1764446994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/5a75e6621715341e08c0a22a319cfc81.mp4?t=1764446994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>解谜要素：</strong> 通过解谜来检验你的逻辑思维和观察能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/a1266e00d0b81cb854e46d4051682255.poster.avif?t=1764446994\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/a1266e00d0b81cb854e46d4051682255.webm?t=1764446994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/a1266e00d0b81cb854e46d4051682255.mp4?t=1764446994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>威胁与陷阱：</strong> 你将遭遇致命的敌人和危险的陷阱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/6a69a28ccfb907c6d6fb24f2ef5637b6.poster.avif?t=1764446994\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/6a69a28ccfb907c6d6fb24f2ef5637b6.webm?t=1764446994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/6a69a28ccfb907c6d6fb24f2ef5637b6.mp4?t=1764446994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>打破循环：</strong> 连续八次成功找出异常，校正扭曲，才能逃离时间循环。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/6d65a18071d384cb336c2855a3c45620.avif?t=1764446994\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras_big/6d65a18071d384cb336c2855a3c45620.avif?t=1764446994 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>预计游玩时间：</strong> 约 3–4 小时，足以发现并体验所有异常现象。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你能否足够信任自己的感官，从循环中逃脱？</strong><br><br><br><br><strong></strong><br><br><br><br><strong>开发者的话：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>RE-EXIT</i> 由一名独立开发者独自制作。非常感谢你的支持与反馈，它们将帮助游戏在今后不断打磨与改进。</p>",
